// NotificationChannel A delivery channel. SECRETS are NEVER returned — the SMTP password, and the slack/webhook URL + token, are write-only. For email channels the NON-secret config is returned so the edit form can pre-fill: smtp_host (also target_hint), smtp_port, from, to, username.
